a_keys
[TITLE]The Manual: Adventure Mode Key Bindings[/TITLE]
Here are the keys you can use to control your adventurer.
[B][B]
[C:7:0:1]Main Keys:[C:7:0:0]
[B]
[IKEY:A_MOVE_S]
[IKEY:A_MOVE_N]
[IKEY:A_MOVE_W]
[IKEY:A_MOVE_E]
[IKEY:A_MOVE_NW]
[IKEY:A_MOVE_NE]
[IKEY:A_MOVE_SW]
[IKEY:A_MOVE_SE]
[IKEY:A_MOVE_UP_AUX]
[IKEY:A_MOVE_DOWN_AUX] - Move/attack.
[B]
[IKEY:A_MOVE_S_UP] etc. - Move/attack up.
[B]
[IKEY:A_MOVE_S_DOWN] etc. - Move/attack down.
[B]
[IKEY:A_CARE_MOVE_S] etc. - Move carefully (for entering water, jumping off cliffs).
[B]
[IKEY:A_MOVE_SAME_SQUARE] - Attack same square.
[B]
[IKEY:A_WAIT] - Wait for ten instants (a normal step).
[R]
[IKEY:A_SHORT_WAIT] - Wait for one instant.
[B]
[IKEY:SELECT] - Advance/clear messages.
[B]
[IKEY:A_ANNOUNCEMENTS] - View announcements.
[B]
[IKEY:A_CONSTRUCTION] - Found a site and build.
[B]
[IKEY:A_COMPANIONS] - View companions.
[B]
[IKEY:A_INV_DROP] - Drop an item.
[B]
[IKEY:A_INV_EATDRINK] - Eat or drink something.
[B]
[IKEY:A_SHOOT] - Fire a projectile.
[B]
[IKEY:A_GROUND] - Pick up an item.
[B]
[IKEY:A_HOLD] - Hold or hang from something (to climb).
[B]
[IKEY:A_INV_LOOK] - Inventory.
[B]
[IKEY:A_JUMP] - Jump.  Sprint in movement options to run and jump.
[B]
[IKEY:A_TALK] - Talk, shout, perform or pray.
[B]
[IKEY:A_LOOK] - Look around.
[B]
[IKEY:A_MOVEMENT] - Movement options.
[B]
[IKEY:A_ODOR] - Show strongest odor.
[B]
[IKEY:A_INV_PUTIN] - Put an item in a container.
[B]
[IKEY:A_INV_DRAW_WEAPON] - Draw/put away weapon.
[B]
[IKEY:A_INV_REMOVE] - Remove an item you are wearing or from a container.
[B]
[IKEY:A_STANCE] - Stand or lie down.
[B]
[IKEY:A_THROW] - Throw an item.
[B]
[IKEY:A_BUILDING] - Interact with a building, furniture, vehicle or mechanism.
[B]
[IKEY:A_CENTER] - Center screen on yourself.
[B]
[IKEY:A_INV_WEAR] - Wear an item.
[B]
[IKEY:A_ACTION] - Create an object, create art, use powers, or butcher a corpse.
[B]
[IKEY:A_YIELD] - Yield.
[B]
[IKEY:A_STATUS] - Status.
[B]
[B]
[IKEY:A_ATTACK] - Aim an attack/wrestle.
[B]
[IKEY:A_COMBAT] - Combat preferences.
[B]
[IKEY:A_DATE] - Date/time.
[B]
[IKEY:A_INTERACT] - Interact with an object in an advanced way.
[B]
[IKEY:A_DISPLAY_TRACKS] - Display all nearby tracks.
[B]
[IKEY:A_FRESHEST_TRACK] - Display information for freshest track.
[B]
[IKEY:A_SEARCH] - Search the nearby area very carefully.
[B]
[IKEY:A_DISPLAY_ODOR] - Display odor information.
[B]
[IKEY:A_TEMPERATURE] - Temperature.
[B]
[IKEY:A_LOG] - Adventure log/information.
[B]
[IKEY:A_SPEED_SNEAK] - Sneak/speed.
[B]
[IKEY:A_TRAVEL] - Travel.
[B]
[IKEY:A_WEATHER] - Weather.
[B]
[IKEY:A_SLEEP] - Sleep/wait.
[B]
[B][B]
[C:7:0:1]Travel Keys:[C:7:0:0]
[B]
[IKEY:CURSOR_DOWN]
[IKEY:CURSOR_UP]
[IKEY:CURSOR_LEFT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_RIGHT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_UPLEFT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_UPRIGHT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_DOWNLEFT]
[IKEY:CURSOR_DOWNRIGHT] - Move.
[B]
[IKEY:CURSOR_UP_Z]
[IKEY:CURSOR_DOWN_Z] - Move into/out of tunnel.
[B]
[IKEY:A_TRAVEL_CLOUDS] - Start/stop cloud viewing.
[B]
[IKEY:A_END_TRAVEL] - Visit location.
[B]
[IKEY:A_TRAVEL_HIDE_INSTRUCTIONS] - Display/hide instructions.
[B]
[IKEY:A_TRAVEL_MAP] - Display/hide map.
[B]
[IKEY:A_SNEAK] - Sneak.
[B]
[IKEY:A_DISPLAY_TRACKS] - Display all nearby tracks and strongest odor.
[B]
[IKEY:A_TRAVEL_LOG] - Adventure log/information.
[B]
[IKEY:A_TRAVEL_SLEEP] - Sleep/wait.
